title: Man Standing Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Person Standing Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A man standing, represented with a medium-dark skin tone. It signifies a person in a standing posture, with a specific skin complexion.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the man standing emoji showcases a figure with a medium-dark skin tone, presented with Apple's renowned attention to realistic lighting and soft, polished surfaces. His upright posture and clear outline convey a feeling of presence, stability, and readiness, commonly used to signify a person's arrival or to simply represent an individual in conversation.
